name: Cute animal counting print
description:
Brighten up your childs room with this fun and educational counting print, Illustrated by Beth Pountney.

'We Love to count!' is signed and printed on quality 250gsm matt paper.

It is perfect for children's rooms and nurseries, and comes rolled in an attrative illustrated gift tube so makes a great present as well.

Printed in an A2 size, to make it easy to frame.

name: Cute  children's Silly sausage Dog Soft Toy
description:
Introducing a lovable little Silly Sausage dog soft toy.

Cuddle up with this cute little Silly Sausage dog.

It is suitable from birth, so makes a lovely new baby gift, or perfect for a first birthday.

Also perfect for any grown up sausage dog fans!

Lovingly designed by Beth Pountney for Jellycat this cute plush toy fits perfectly with Beth's silly sausage board book.

Made from soft strokable brown fabric, Silly Sausage has a soft underbelly and floppy ears with a soft black nose to cuddle up too.

His big puppy dog eyes are cheeky and match the same character in Silly sausage board book.

Silly Sausage measures 10 inches long and can be hand washed.

name: Cute individual  framed animal letters
description:
Create your child's name as a piece of wall art with these gorgeous framed animal letters.

Spell a name or buy an initial, these cute images are come in a choice of three coloured backgrounds  and framed in a high quality white frame designed to fit in with any bedroom decor.

Each letter has been lovingly designed by illustrator Beth Pountney, with six animal characters including two cheeky monkeys, a friendly looking zebra and some tall giraffes and a baby elephant.

Each frame is made in the UK and measures 12 x 12 cm with the image measuring 8 x 8 cm. Each frame can be hung or will stand alone.
